Functional:

The system must have a control system.

The system must have a collision system.

The system must have strict bounds.

The system must allow acceleration/de

The system must have a winning feature if obstacles avoided.

The system must have a losing feature if obstacle hit.

The system must support at least 1 player.

Non-Functional:

The system must have clearly shown bounds.

The system must have entities driving related for obstacles.

The system must have entity for at least 1 player.
